.SH INSTANCE METHODS
.TP
\f[B]XMLHttpRequest.abort()\f[R]
Aborts the request if it has already been sent.
.TP
\f[B]XMLHttpRequest.getAllResponseHeaders()\f[R]
Returns all the response headers, separated by CRLF, as a string, or
\f[CR]null\f[R] if no response has been received.
.TP
\f[B]XMLHttpRequest.getResponseHeader()\f[R]
Returns the string containing the text of the specified header, or
\f[CR]null\f[R] if either the response has not yet been received or the
header doesn\(cqt exist in the response.
.TP
\f[B]XMLHttpRequest.open()\f[R]
